John C. Scoccola



Mr. John C. Scoccola is Independent Director at Stewardship Financial Corp. and Manager-Solution Architect at NYNEX Long Distance Co. He is on the Board of Directors at Atlantic Stewardship Bank and Stewardship Financial Corp. 
He received his undergraduate degree from New Jersey Institute of Technology.



