Home







John C. Miller



John C. Miller
Posted on March 28, 2016 

John C. MillerDivision DirectorJohn Miller is the Division Director for the Bayou Division of Coca-Cola UNITED. He graduated from LSU in 1988 with a degree in Finance. John began his career at Coca-Cola in 2002. Prior to Division Director, John has held the positions of Management Trainee, Bulk Distribution Manager, On-Premise Manager and Division Vice-President. He has also been awarded the 2007 Marketer of the Year for SMEI.
John is married to Graham Wetherbee Miller and has three children, Mary Madalyn, Clyde, and Maggie. They are members of First United Methodist Church of Baton Rouge and the Walk to Emmaus Community. John serves as a board member at the Better Business Bureau, Baton Rouge Area Chamber of Commerce, Louisiana Arts & Science Center, Louisiana Sports Foundation and LSU Football Camps.

 





 

